# Unicity KPI Briefing System — Project Context

> Auto-generated by setup-skills. Keep updated as the project evolves.

## What this is
Morning KPI briefing system for Unicity Solar Energy. Vercel-deployed Vite
React SPA + serverless API that:
- Pulls live pipeline data from Pipedrive at 6am ET weekdays
- Generates personalised HTML briefing emails for up to 30 team members
- Dashboard at https://unicity-kpi.vercel.app

## Key constraints
- No GitHub auth for Claude — code ships as zip files or inline PowerShell writes.
- Repo lives at C:\UnicityDev\Unitea
- Windows PowerShell. Absolute paths for Copy-Item -Destination. Never ../
- Vercel free tier — serverless functions, Vercel Blob, no DB.
- Stephen is non-technical. Trust the tooling.

## Stack
| Layer | Tech |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React 19, TypeScript, Vite 8 |
| Backend | Vercel serverless (@vercel/node) |
| Email | Gmail API via OAuth2 |
| Pipeline data | Pipedrive REST API |
| Persistence | Vercel Blob (kpi-tags config, daily snapshots) |
| Auth | Google OAuth (sign-in), CRON_SECRET (cron auth) |
| CI | GitHub Actions (tsc + vitest on PRs) |
| Tests | Vitest, 136+ tests |

